    "Name": "Hogo-Sha HGS-A211",
    "Details": "The Hogo-sha HGS-A211 mixes close-range firepower across a heavily armored 85-ton industrial frame. A PPC in the right arm provides the primary punch while twin Machine Guns handle infantry. The left arm carries a Fluid Gun and Flamer for crowd control work. An SRM 6 in the left torso adds burst damage at close range. Two Small Lasers and a Searchlight sit in the right torso. Full environmental sealing enables operations in hostile atmospheres.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Lifesupport</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.88</color></b>",
